194
00:13:56,330 --> 00:13:58,870
<font size='30'>මේ... ම්ම්...</font>

195
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,000
<font size='30'>රූඩෝ?</font>

196
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,820
<font size='30'>ඒහ්?</font>

197
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,700
<font size='30'>ඒ පුලුන් පුරවපු සතාl...</font>

