217
00:16:43,370 --> 00:16:45,210
<font size='30'>...උඹ...</font>

218
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,240
<font size='30'>රූඩෝ...</font>

219
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,370
<font size='30'>...දුවන්න...</font>

220
00:16:51,370 --> 00:16:52,360
<font size='30'>රෙග්ටෝ...</font>

221
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:56,490
<font size='30'>යන්න... දුවන්න...</font>

222
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:53,990
<font size='30'>රෙග්ටෝ!</font>

223
00:16:55,290 --> 00:16:56,490
